data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated home. The first floor boasts of new windows that lets the natural light permeate throughout the living and dinning rooms. The intimate kitchen has plenty of counter outlets, new cabinets and countertops and brand new stainless steel appliances. Off the kitchen you will find your laundry room ready for you to bring your washer & dryer. A half bath completes the first floor. The second floor offers 4 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The third floor is finished and can be used as an additional bedroom, office, playroom or additional living space. The possibilities are endless. While the basement isn't finished, it is clean, dry and painted. The rear yard screams entertainment worthy! Come and see it for yourself. Uncover the perfect blend of classic charm and modern luxury in this meticulously crafted 5-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom residence spanning 1692 sq ft. Your dream home is here, and it's more captivating than ever! Step into a world where every detail matters. While the main roof remains steadfast, the front porch and back addition boast brand-new roofs, ensuring both durability and style. Electrical: Experience safety and efficiency with all copper wires. Plumbing: Enjoy worry-free living with PEX piping and PVC for sewer lines. HVAC: Revel in year-round comfort with brand-new furnace and AC units. Water Heater: Indulge in endless hot showers with a state-of-the-art water heater.  Bonus Inclusion: Free 1-year Home Warranty!
